<br />
<p class="text-center"> It's the last day of August, the weather is slowly cooling, and Labor Day is a few days away! What a perfect weekend to come the Garden!</p>
<br/>


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/eupatorium-maculatum-gateway-hms18.jpg" alt="Gateway Spotted Joe Pye Weed" title="Gateway Spotted Joe Pye Weed" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Gateway Spotted Joe Pye Weed &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Eupatorium maculatum</i> 'Gateway'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> This towering perennial adds a wonderful contrast around the pond in the Water Pavilion.</p>
<br />


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/kniphofia-christmas-cheer-hms18.jpg" alt="Christmas Cheer Poker" title="Christmas Cheer Poker" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Christmas Cheer Poker &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Kniphofia</i> 'Christmas Cheer'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> This bright poker can be seen blooming in the Water Conservation Garden.</p>
<br />


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/hibiscus-disco-bell-mix-hms18.jpg" alt="Disco Bell Hibiscus" title="Disco Bell Hibiscus" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Disco Bell Hibiscus &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Hibiscus</i> 'Disco Bell Mix'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> This flower is as big as a human head! Can be seen along the Floral Walk.</p>
<br />


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/eucomis-sparkling-burgundy-hms18.jpg" alt="Pineapple Lily" title="Pineapple Lily" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Pineapple Lily &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Eucomis</i> 'Sparkling Burgundy'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> This bulb in the Water Pavilion is just beginning to bloom! Hurry and get up here to catch it's full bloom! </p>
<br />


<img src="/images/blogs/whats-blooming-blog/2018-08-31/rosa-playboy-hms18.jpg" alt="Playboy Rose" title="Playboy Rose" class="img-center responsive" style="max-width: 600px;" />
<h5 class="text-center">Playboy Rose &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i> Rosa</i> 'Playboy'</h5>
<p class="text-center"> If you hang out near this shrub in the Rose Garden, you will get an eyeful of bees! </p>
<br />


<p class="text-center"> This Labor Day, take a break from the grind by spending a few hours up here at Red Butte Garden. Your senses will thank you!</p>
<br />

<p class="text-center"> And don't forget about our LegoÂ® Nature Connects Display! It will only be in the Garden for a couple more weeks!</p>
